<div1 type="letter">

<pb facs="nei.j4c.46.12-13_0001a" />

<note type="curatorial">Aly Collection

231-1</note>
   
<opener>
<dateline>June 14, '65</dateline>


<salute>Dear Lucile:</salute>
</opener>
<p>It has just struck me that you might be able to use me out there in connection with the biography. If so, I <hi rend="underline">could</hi> come awhile. This
is <hi rend="double underline">not</hi> <hi rend="underline">to be regarded as a request for an invitation</hi>(!) <del>;</del> I just want you to know I'd be

<pb facs="nei.j4c.46.12-13_0001b"/>

available. I feel it's late to tell you this, but I hadn't thought of it. I suspect that you are already tied up for the summer.</p>

<p>This carries affection to each of you &#8212; <hi rend="underline">and</hi> the sweet puppy too.</p>

<p>I seem to have lost Bower for the moment; Tell him a big hello from me.</p>
<closer>
&#8212; <signed>John</signed>.
</closer>

<fw type="curatorial">12</fw>

<postscript>
<p>I've just seen the cover for <hi rend="underline">Lyric and Dramatic Poems</hi>.</p>
</postscript>

